## Limitations
This analysis is limited by the availability of recent data and legal rulings. The evolving nature of the COVID-19 pandemic and related policies means that new developments could alter the current understanding of vaccine mandates and discrimination. Additionally, the focus on English-language sources may exclude relevant perspectives from non-English speaking regions.